---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | ReadRadar">
    <Section id="about-header" title="About ReadRadar" icon="i">
        <div class="mt-12 neo-card p-8 md:p-12 border-l-4 border-secondary">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 uppercase">Mission</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-body text-lg mb-8">
                ReadRadar is the intelligence layer for technical resources. As the pace of AI research and engineering accelerates, relying on static curated lists is no longer viable. Our mission is to build an autonomous discovery engine that tracks, validates, and indexes the books, papers, and repositories shaping the future of technology.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 uppercase mt-12 border-t-2 border-border pt-12">Architecture</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-body text-lg mb-6">
                ReadRadar employs a decoupled, agent-first architecture:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-4 text-gray-300 font-mono text-sm mb-8">
                <li><strong class="text-primary">Agent Layer:</strong> Autonomous crawlers and evaluators continuously scan sources (GitHub, ArXiv, Twitter) for high-signal resources.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-secondary">Data Layer:</strong> Validated resources are committed to structured JSON files acting as a transparent database.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-danger">UI Layer:</strong> This frontend (Astro + Tailwind) strictly consumes the data layer statically, guaranteeing instant loads and zero backend overhead.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 uppercase mt-12 border-t-2 border-border pt-12">Open Source</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-body text-lg">
                ReadRadar is fully open source under the MIT License. We believe the intelligence layer for AI should be transparent, verifiable, and collectively owned.
            </p>
            
            <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="https://github.com/Hardik-Sankhla/ReadRadar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white text-black font-bold font-heading px-8 py-4 uppercase shadow-neo hover:shadow-neo hover:translate-y-1 hover:translate-x-1 transition-all border-2 border-border">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-6 h-6 fill-current"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
                    View Repository
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Section>
</Layout>
